--- ROOT -- function onReceiveOSC(message, connections) if message[1] == '/device_name' then local device_name = message[2][1].value device_name_control = root:findByName('DEVICE_NAME_CONTROL', true) device_name_control.values['text'] = device_name end
if message[1] == '/device_address' then local device_address = message[2][1].value device_name_control.values['text'] = device_name_control.values['text'] .. " (" .. device_address .. ")" end end

local selfOrigin = 0 local encoderOrigin = 0 local shouldSetOrigin = false local encoder = self.parent.children["encoder"]
function onValueChanged(valueName) if (valueName == "touch" and self.values.touch) then shouldSetOrigin = true end
if (valueName == "x") then if (shouldSetOrigin) then shouldSetOrigin = false selfOrigin = self.values.x encoderOrigin = encoder.values.x else delta = (selfOrigin - self.values.x) * .025 encoder.values.x = encoderOrigin - delta end end end

local text = self.parent.children["text"] local text255 = self.parent.children["text255"]
function onValueChanged(valueName) if (valueName == "x") then local truncated = self.values.x * 1000 text.values.text = tostring(math.floor(truncated) / 1000.0) text255.values.text = math.floor(self.values.x * 255) end end
